article.description: — Ledarrius Brewer tossed in 17 points as East Tennessee State defeated Murray State 66-58 on Monday.
article.headline: Brewer leads East Tennessee St past Murray St 66-58
article.linkText: Brewer leads East Tennessee St past Murray St 66-58
article.story: NAPLES, Fla. -- — Ledarrius Brewer tossed in 17 points as East Tennessee State defeated Murray State 66-58 on Monday. Charlie Weber had 13 points for the Buccaneers (2-2), while David Sloan scored 11. KJ Williams had 18 points and 10 rebounds for the Racers (3-1). Tevin Brown added 12 points and seven boards.
